### **3. 32_LogBurstRadar**  
**Description:**  
Detects bursts of activity and frequent lines in large log files.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogBurstRadar - Log Frequency & Spike Analyzer

LogBurstRadar parses log files to find common lines and timestamped anomalies that may indicate instability or attack.

## Features
- Repetition clustering  
- Burst detection  
- Keyword filter  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/32_LogBurstRadar.git
cd 32_LogBurstRadar
python analyze.py logs/app.log
